Detailed Description

RTP session settings.

Field Documentation

pj_uint8_t pjmedia_rtp_session_setting::flags

Bitmask flags to specify whether such field is set. Bitmask contents are: (bit #0 is LSB) bit #0: default payload type bit #1: sender SSRC bit #2: sequence bit #3: timestamp

int pjmedia_rtp_session_setting::default_pt

Default payload type.

Sender SSRC.

Sequence.

Timestamp.
